{"type": "article", "id": 26858, "title": "皮革背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-16T06:45:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702162528hRKbAn1rlqp97BoO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>出门旅行时，不少人一定有过在机场安检手忙脚乱地将笔记本电脑拿出拿进的经历，以制作为科技产品打造的配件闻名的洛杉矶品牌 <a href=\"http://thisisground.com/\">This Is Ground</a> 最近就推出了一款试图解决这一烦恼的皮革背包。它内置一个专门为笔记本电脑设计的托盘，让你不必再拿出设备即可通过安检。这款外形时尚的背包有多层储物空间，拉链口袋里还专门为各类连接线和手机配备了皮带，对于整理控来说也是一大福音。所有背包均为手工制作，售价 750 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"http://thisisground.com/products/venture?variant=16747417349\">链接</a>购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162526p8vVbFTk96aNXhSD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021625267cShzOmw9tlHbk4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702162528Yh26wKOZPFRmNktJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}